kw.doc: Closes all open browsers and resets the browser cache.

kw.doc: Opens a new browser instance to given URL.

kw.name: Comment
kw.doc: Displays the given messages in the log file as keyword arguments.

kw.name: Set Window Position
kw.doc: Sets the position `x` and `y` of the current window to the specified values.

kw.name: Set Window Size
kw.doc: Sets the `width` and `height` of the current window to the specified values.

kw.name: Wait Until Page Contains Element
kw.doc: Waits until element specified with `locator` appears on current page.

kw.name: Capture Page Screenshot
kw.doc: Takes a screenshot of the current page and embeds it into the log.
